aws_services: CloudTrail, RDS, EC2, IAM, S3, VPC
training_quality_justification: High-value training data demonstrating common CDKTF Java pitfalls including API versioning, security best practices (password generation), multi-AZ architecture, and proper resource configuration. The model showed good architectural understanding but failed on critical implementation details, making this excellent data for improving practical IaC skills.
